name: BabyCakes Israel
tag_list: baby-clothing, baby-products, babies, baby-cakes, gifts, parenting
overview: BabyCakes Gift Boutique is an Israeli market leader in the baby products and gifts for newborns and their mothers. BabyCakes has set itself the goal of providing best quality products and the most original gifts in unique and fun packaging aside to personal and pleasant service. Everything in the shop is made especially for the Babycakes brand and under BabyCakes restrictions which assures the highest quality and safety for the baby. BabyCakes offers baby clothing, sweet bouquets of chocolates and candy, gift packages of natural beauty products, and the amazing and unique diaper babycakes. There is an actual store in Rishpon, Israel, as well as online store with unique online sales and home delivery.
